commit f9b82bc64a9405e486575c65c1729229eb0a8198
Author: Jia Tan <jiat0218@gmail.com>
Date:   2023-12-15 16:56:31 +0800

    CI: Update Upload Artifact Action.

 .github/workflows/ci.yml         | 2 +-
 .github/workflows/windows-ci.yml | 2 +-
